%3E%3Cspan%3E).%20Because%20of%20this%2C%20I'm%20unsure%20if%20this%20will%20work%20for%20those%20with%20the%20deepest%20complexions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20ordered%20shade%20%26quot%3B201%20Fair.%26quot%3B%20When%20I%20first%20opened%20the%20box%2C%20I%20loved%20how%20simple%20and%20sleek%20the%20packaging%20was.%20What's%20more%2C%20the%20ultra-soft%20built-in%20brush%20actually%20felt%20like%20something%20I%20would%20use%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-travel-makeup-bag%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etraveling%20with%20makeup%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUpon%20my%20first%20application%2C%20the%20product%20felt%20a%20lot%20creamier%20on%20my%20skin%20than%20expected.%20I%20immediately%20disliked%20its%20powdery%20floral%20scent%20%E2%80%94%20which%20thankfully%20doesn't%20come%20from%20any%20added%20perfume%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20more%20likely%20due%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ejasmine%3Cspan%3E%20and%20evening%20primrose%20oils.%20Still%2C%20the%20heavy%20fragrance%20is%20my%20least%20favorite%20aspect%20of%20the%20formula.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22824cced4-645f-4e12-8a36-d158269338f3%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EBefore%20and%20after%20blending%20out%20the%20color-changing%20foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20before%20after%20view%20of%20the%20author%20wearing%20El%20Roel%20foundation%20stick.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a366c8cfc04e97619b94f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20El%20Roel%20Blanc%20Cover%20Cream%20Stick%20swatches%20white%2C%20but%20blends%20away%20to%20reveal%20a%20near-perfect%20color%20match.%3Cp%3EOlivia%20Rose%20Rushing%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20like%20the%20viral%20TikTok%20videos%2C%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20how%20intensely%20stark%20white%20the%20color%20was%20swatched%20against%20my%20complexion%20(and%20I'm%20quite%20fair%20to%20begin%20with).%20That%20being%20said%2C%20it%20started%20to%20blend%20away%20relatively%20effortlessly%2C%20slowly%20but%20surely%20revealing%20an%20impressive%20color%20match%20that's%20hard%20to%20find%20in%20a%20foundation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20I%20initially%20thought%20that%20the%20built-in%20brush%20would%20be%20a%20major%20win%2C%20I%20did%20find%20that%20it%20took%20much%20longer%20than%20I%20prefer%20to%20spend%20blending%20my%20base%20makeup.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20I%20probably%20wouldn't%20use%20it%20again%2C%20unless%20I%20was%20traveling%20or%20in%20a%20pinch%20as%20it%20did%20a%20good%20enough%20job.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e51c95a7-5f37-4a56-a32b-e36f1dedf800%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20matched%20my%20skin%20tone%20beautifully%2C%20but%20I%20just%20can't%20get%20past%20the%20scent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20the%20color%20match%20is%20almost%20exact%2C%20and%20with%20a%20surprising%20amount%20of%20coverage%20that%20doesn't%20require%20you%20to%20layer%20more%20swipes%20of%20foundation.%20And%20as%20many%20have%20noted%20online%2C%20the%20final%20result%20is%20a%20soft-matte%20finish%20with%20a%20pretty%20glow%20that%20appears%20healthy%20and%20nourished%20thanks%20to%20efficacious%20ingredients%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eniacinamide%3Cspan%3E.%20In%20that%20regard%3A%20I%20totally%20understand%20the%20hype.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20also%20loved%20how%20this%20foundation%20worked%20well%20with%20my%20current%20product%20lineup%2C%20like%20my%20go-to%20cream-to-powder%20blush%20that's%20coloring%20my%20cheeks.%20Though%20honestly%2C%20despite%20its%20light%20finish%2C%20it%20was%20weighed%20down%20by%20the%20lingering%20powdery%20jasmine%20aroma.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d1c6f52-0da8-445b-9f3f-3487908ac349%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Elroel%20foundation%20stick%20does%20exactly%20what%20it%20promises%3A%20it%20swipes%20on%20white%2C%20blends%20into%20skin%20for%20a%20wow-worthy%20color%20match%2C%20and%20leaves%20you%20looking%20youthfully%20dewy.%20It%20never%20made%20my%20skin%20look%20too%20textured%20or%20caky%2C%20and%20overall%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-lightweight-foundations%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eformula%20is%20lightweight%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20wears%20well%20throughout%20the%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20said%2C%20my%20main%20gripes%20are%20the%20limited%20shade%20range%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20for%20those%20with%20darker%20skin%20tones%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20scent%2C%20which%20is%20a%20personal%20preference%20but%20important%20to%20note.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20it%20hasn't%20replaced%20my%20current%20foundation%2C%20though%20it%20might%20just%20end%20up%20being%20someone%20else's%20new%20holy%20grail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Felroel-foundation-stick-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755545170000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a36c49cfc04e97619b955a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Felroel-foundation-stick-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20my%20Elroel%20foundation%20stick%20review%2C%20I%20tested%20the%20viral%20color-changing%20formula%20on%20my%20fair%20skin%20for%20its%20shade%20matching%2C%20blendability%2C%20and%20finish.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Olivia%20Rose%20Rushing)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Felroel-foundation-stick-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Some%20travel%20advisors%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20plan%20trips%20and%20boost%20business%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20they're%20not%20afraid%20they'll%20be%20replaced%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20desk%20agent%20hands%20a%20person%20a%20passport%20and%20a%20boarding%20pass.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a3494da17a8c5b4053074f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPersonalized%20in-room%20perks%20and%20free%20upgrades%20are%20some%20of%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20travel%20agents.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Photos%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2F%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20travel%20agents%20are%20leveraging%20AI%20tools%20to%20plan%20trips%20more%20efficiently%20and%20increase%20bookings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20said%20AI%20can't%20replace%20the%20personal%20touch%20and%20expertise%20of%20travel%20agents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fhow-ai-is-changing-everything%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20AI%20Is%20Changing%20Everything%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20on%20AI%20adoption%20across%20industries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDecades%20ago%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-agents-back-gen-z-millennials-vacation-planning-overseas-resorts-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20held%20the%20keys%20to%20the%20world%2C%20crafting%20and%20coordinating%20trips%20for%20the%20everyday%20traveler.%20Then%20came%20Expedia%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20other%20online%20booking%20behemoths%20that%20shifted%20control%20directly%20to%20consumers%2C%20forcing%20agents%20to%20adapt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20another%20disruption%20has%20arrived%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-artificial-intelligence-customer-experience-business-applications-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20while%20its%20ability%20to%20plan%20travel%20may%20have%20some%20agents%20feeling%20fearful%20once%20more%2C%20a%20new%20wave%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-travel-advisors-on-industry-popularity-career-opportunities-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20advisors%3C%2Fa%3E%20see%20AI%20not%20as%20a%20threat%2C%20but%20a%20tool.%20And%20they're%20leaning%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bab4fa80-dd3a-4440-80c3-ce88c1818835%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBooking%20travel%20with%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAthena%20Livadas%20owns%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pame.travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EP%C3%A1me%20Travel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20specializes%20in%20booking%20five-star%20luxury%20travel.%20She%20uses%20AI%20daily%20to%20come%20up%20with%20high-level%20thoughts%20on%20routes%20or%20destinations%2C%20write%20emails%20faster%2C%20and%20drive%20her%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20travel%20advisors%20don't%20see%20the%20need%2C%20or%20even%20get%20offended%2C%20when%20AI%20is%20brought%20up%20in%20the%20context%20of%20travel%20planning.%20But%20I%20couldn't%20disagree%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20replacing%20us.%20It's%20a%20tool%20that%20gives%20advisors%20super%20powers%20to%20deliver%20even%20more%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20according%20to%20her%20metrics%2C%20it's%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20look%20at%20a%20six-month%20period%20before%20and%20after%20I%20started%20using%20AI%2C%20my%20business%20has%20grown%20about%2040%25%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%20there%20are%20other%20factors%20involved%2C%20but%20the%20time%20AI%20saves%20me%20has%20definitely%20been%20a%20contributing%20reason.%20It%20has%20freed%20me%20up%20to%20take%20on%20more%20clients%20and%20focus%20on%20marketing%20and%20outreach%20efforts%20that%20actually%20drive%20business%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there's%20no%20data%20yet%20on%20industry-wide%20adoption%20of%20AI%20tools%2C%20it's%20clear%20Livadas%20isn't%20the%20only%20one%20getting%20a%20boost%20from%20the%20technology.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foratravel.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFora%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20digital%20travel%20agency%20with%20hundreds%20of%20advisors%20around%20the%20world%2C%20integrates%20AI%20internally%20in%20its%20own%20proprietary%20platforms%20where%20most%20advisors%20use%20it%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFora%20began%20rolling%20out%20AI-powered%20tools%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jake%20Peters%2C%20the%20company's%20cofounder%20and%20chief%20product%20and%20technology%20officer.%20%26quot%3BThese%20tools%20are%20integrated%20directly%20into%20the%20advisor%20workflow%2C%20whether%20it's%20drafting%20proposals%2C%20building%20itineraries%2C%20or%20creating%20marketing%20content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20tool%2C%20for%20example%2C%20helps%20format%20text%20to%20be%20easier%20to%20read%20and%20more%20client-friendly.%20%26quot%3BThis%20feature%20is%20used%2070%25%20of%20the%20time%20when%20we%20are%20showing%20rates%20in%20our%20booking%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20Peters%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-chatbots-like-chatgpt-work-explainer-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echatbot%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20Sidekick%2C%20which%20Fora%20has%20trained%20on%20all%20of%20its%20proprietary%20information%2C%20including%20trainings%2C%20help%20center%20articles%2C%20and%20hotel%20and%20destination%20information.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20used%20by%2025%25%20of%20advisors%20each%20month%2C%20and%2035%25%20of%20advisors%20who%20are%20new%20to%20Fora%2C%26quot%3B%20Peters%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERita%20Carton%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foratravel.com%2Fadvisor%2Frita-carton%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20advisor%20with%20Fora%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20estimates%20that%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Fora's%20internal%20tools%20and%20strategic%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20research%20%E2%80%94%20reduces%20her%20average%20trip%20planning%20time%20by%2050%25%2C%20cuts%20her%20client%20response%20time%20in%20half%2C%20and%20has%20increased%20bookings%20three%20times%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BA%20year%20ago%2C%20I%20could%20only%20manage%20two%20to%20three%20trips%20at%20a%20time%20and%20maybe%20five%20a%20quarter%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Q1%20of%20this%20year%2C%20I%20successfully%20handled%20nine%20simultaneous%20trips%2C%20tripling%20my%20capacity%20without%20compromising%20service%20quality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229fe79344-990d-4f55-8a1f-b51e3b3fad2e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20may%20be%20helpful%2C%20but%20it%20can't%20do%20it%20all%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20or%20not%20other%20agents%20agree%20on%20the%20need%20to%20embrace%20AI%2C%20it's%20surely%20influencing%20how%20consumers%20plan%20travel.%20A%20Deloitte%20survey%20conducted%20from%20October%202023%20to%20October%202024%20found%20that%20the%20share%20of%20respondents%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deloitte.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Finsights%2Farticles%2F2024%2Fus187627_cic-holiday-travel%2F2024-Deloitte-Holiday-Travel-Study.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eused%20generative%20AI%20for%20trip%20planning%3C%2Fa%3E%20doubled%20from%208%25%20to%2016%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20we're%20at%20a%20similar%20age%20with%20AI%20that%20we%20were%20when%20the%20internet%20started%20to%20boom%2C%26quot%3B%20Livadas%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20either%20adapt%20and%20learn%20how%20to%20use%20it%20to%20better%20your%20outputs%20for%20clients%2C%20or%20you'll%20be%20left%20behind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Livadas%20doesn't%20think%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20replace%20travel%20agents%20anytime%20soon.%20She%20warned%20that%20travelers%20should%20expect%20to%20get%20common%2C%20generic%20travel%20advice%20from%20AI%20rather%20than%20the%20off-the-beaten-path%2C%20hidden%20gems%20that%20travel%20agents%20can%20help%20uncover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20if%20you're%20planning%20a%20trip%20to%20Japan%2C%20it'll%20probably%20spit%20out%20the%20usual%20Tokyo%20to%20Kyoto%20to%20Osaka%20route%20with%20big%20chain-brand%20hotels%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20I%20were%20building%20the%20itinerary%20and%20I%20knew%20the%20client%20loved%20surfing%2C%20I%20would%20include%20Kamakura%2C%20a%20small%20fishing%20village%20with%20a%20mellow%20longboard%20wave%20that's%20perfect%20in%20summer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20examples%2C%20she%20said%2C%20are%20exactly%20the%20kind%20of%20tailored%20touches%20AI%20routinely%20overlooks%20that%20travel%20advisors%20weave%20into%20itineraries%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20disconnect%20is%20directly%20aligned%20with%20the%20one%20major%20thing%20AI%20can't%20replicate.%20%26quot%3BThe%20travel%20agency%20is%20all%20about%20relationships%2C%26quot%3B%20Carton%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20go%20directly%20to%20the%20hotel%20after%20we%20book%20to%20get%20the%20manager%2C%20and%20I%20cannot%20tell%20you%20how%20many%20clients%20have%20told%20me%20they%20got%20upgraded%20or%20had%20surprises%20in%20the%20room%20as%20a%20result.%20You%20can't%20do%20that%20yourself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20personalized%20in-room%20perks%2C%20free%20upgrades%2C%20and%20moments%20meant%20to%20delight%20are%20hallmarks%20of%20the%20travel%20agent's%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20value%20we%20bring%20is%20relationship-driven%2C%20and%20that%20will%20never%20go%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Livadas%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20personally%20know%20general%20managers%20of%20five-star%20luxury%20properties%20all%20over%20the%20world%20that%20will%20welcome%20my%20guests%20upon%20arrival%20with%20a%20personalized%20gift%20from%20me.%20How%20can%20a%20bot%20do%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-travel-agents-trip-planning-agency-business-growth-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755544967000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a3494da17a8c5b4053074f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-travel-agents-trip-planning-agency-business-growth-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20consumers%20begin%20using%20AI%20for%20trip%20planning%2C%20some%20travel%20agents%20are%20embracing%20the%20tech%2C%20saving%20time%20and%20boosting%20bookings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ehochberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Emily%20Hochberg)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-travel-agents-trip-planning-agency-business-growth-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Row%20Over%20No%20Mention%20Of%20Kuki%20Militants%20In%20Answer%20Choices%20On%20Manipur%20Crisis%2C%20Assam%20Panel%20Points%20At%20Question%20Setters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20Assam%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(APSC)%20h