%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.federalregister.gov%2Fdocuments%2F2025%2F08%2F18%2F2025-15665%2Fwilliam-d-ford-federal-direct-loan-direct-loan-program%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20narrow%20eligibility%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-public-service-loan-forgiveness-student-debt-relief-plans-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPublic%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E%20program%20on%20Monday.%20The%20public%20comment%20period%20%E2%80%94%20during%20which%20anyone%20can%20submit%20comments%20on%20the%20new%20regulations%20to%20the%20administration%20%E2%80%94%20is%20officially%20open%20through%20September%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPSLF%2C%20which%20is%20intended%20to%20forgive%20student%20debt%20for%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20workers%20after%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments%2C%20has%20allowed%20for%20the%20discharge%20of%20over%20a%20billion%20dollars%20in%20student%20debt%20for%20public%20servants.%20Trump%20is%20seeking%20to%20alter%20the%20program%20%E2%80%94%20he%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20in%20March%20asking%20the%20education%20secretary%20to%20redefine%20what%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20service%26quot%3B%20means%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-public-service-loan-forgiveness-program-pslf-education-department-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eremove%20PSLF%20eligibility%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20employers%20engaging%20in%20%26quot%3Banti-American%26quot%3B%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20rule%20to%20limit%20PSLF%2C%20published%20in%20the%20Federal%20Register%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bin%20cases%20where%20an%20employer%20is%20deemed%20to%20have%20engaged%20in%20activities%20that%20breach%20federal%20or%20state%20law%20or%20established%20public%20policy%2C%20affected%20borrowers%20would%20no%20longer%20receive%20credit%20toward%20loan%20forgiveness%20for%20months%20worked%20after%20the%20effective%20date%20of%20ineligibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20may%20delay%20or%20prevent%20forgiveness%20for%20a%20subset%20of%20borrowers%2C%20the%20overall%20design%20of%20the%20regulations%E2%80%94including%20advance%20notice%2C%20transparency%20around%20determinations%2C%20and%20employer%20recertification%20pathways%E2%80%94helps%20mitigate%20unexpected%20harm%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20rule%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompromising%20behavior%20by%20an%20employer%2C%20according%20to%20the%20rule%2C%20could%20include%20violation%20of%20the%20federal%20disabilities%20act%3B%20violation%20of%20federal%20immigration%20law%3B%20what%20the%20department%20characterizes%20as%20%26quot%3Bchemical%20castration%20or%20mutilation%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20the%20use%20of%20puberty%20blockers%20or%20hormones%20to%20help%20a%20transgender%20person%20transition%3B%20and%20acts%20of%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Education%20held%20negotiation%20sessions%20with%20stakeholders%20in%20early%20July%2C%20and%20some%20members%20of%20the%20committee%20expressed%20concerns%20with%20the%20department's%20intent%20to%20limit%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20intent%20of%20Congress%20was%20not%20to%20narrow%20the%20eligibility%2C%26quot%3B%20Betsy%20Mayotte%2C%20the%20president%20of%20The%20Institute%20of%20Student%20Loan%20Advisors%20and%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Erepresentative%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%2C%20said%20during%20a%20session.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20to%20make%20it%20as%20expansive%20as%20possible%20under%20the%20statute%20that%20they%20wrote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20of%20the%20administration%20argued%20that%20the%20education%20secretary%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20interpret%20regulations%20and%20statutes%20and%20can%20legally%20refine%20PSLF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudent-loan%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20PSLF%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Trump's%20plans%20to%20change%20a%20program%20they