d%20biodegradable%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mistry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETBC%20has%20patented%20both%20its%20technology%20and%20the%20process%20involved.%20This%20protection%20helps%20safeguard%20its%20intellectual%20property%20and%20ensures%20that%20the%20alt-leather%20start-up%20continues%20to%20lead%20in%20the%20development%20of%20eco-friendly%20alternatives%20to%20traditional%20leather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20is%20tomato%20leather%20made%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20launching%20its%20first%20product%2C%20%E2%80%98Original%20Bioleather%E2%80%99%2C%20in%202019%2C%20the%20company%20has%20committed%20to%20making%20affordable%20leather%20that%20is%20vegan%2C%20carbon-neutral%2C%20biodegradable%2C%20and%20dyed%20with%20all-natural%20dyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20this%20today%2C%20TBC%20sources%20tomato%20waste%20from%20local%20food%20processing%20units%20and%20farms%2C%20in%20regions%20where%20tomatoes%20are%20grown%20in%20abundance%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20by-products%20would%20otherwise%20go%20to%20waste%2C%20so%2C%20we%20form%20partnerships%20with%20suppliers%20to%20collect%20and%20repurpose%20them%20into%20a%20valuable%20resource%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mistry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20Surat%20plant%2C%20Bioleather%20is%20crafted%20using%20tomato%20by-products%2C%20combined%20with%20biopolymers%2C%20plant-based%20binders%2C%20and%20natural%20fibers.%20The%20process%20involves%20blending%20these%20components%2C%20followed%20by%20non-toxic%20curing%20to%20achieve%20a%20durable%2C%20leather-like%20texture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDAIG5FoxykN%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDAIG5FoxykN%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig